

Pre-requisite to change settings in the server:

1. Each and every folder has a cron and a log section. Cron is called by the cronjob in the server. Logs are used to store log and then send email to the receipents.
2. password for all the microservices and other sources are kept inside /opt/credential/pass.sh.
3. Change the pass.sh file if the credentials are added / changed.

